TM TT LUN VN THC S
ti: Tm hiu cng ngh web a phng tin v ng dng
Tc gi lun vn: Nguyn Mnh Cng Kha: 2012A
Ngi hng dn: PGS.TS. Nguyn Th Hong Lan
Ni dung tm tt:
a, L do chn ti
Xut pht t nhu cu tm kim thng tin ti liu phc v nghin cu v hc tp
ti thc hin ti lun vn Tm hiu v cng ngh web a phng tin v ng dng.
Vi mc ch xy dng h thng CSDL ti liu a phng tin cho website trng i
hc SPKT Hng Yn.
Tm hiu v cng ngh web a phng tin v nghin cu xy dng ng dng
qun tr CSDL ti liu a phng tin cho cho php tm kim, download v upload CSDL
ti liu a phng tin cho website ca trng HSPKT Hng yn
.
b, Mc ch nghin cu ca lun vn, i tng, phm vi nghin cu
Mc ch nghin cu
xy dng ng dng qun tr CSDL ti liu a phng tin cho php tm kim,
download v upload CSDL ti liu a phng tin cho website ca trng HSPKT
Hng yn
i tng nghin cu:
- Cng ngh web a phng tin
- Qun tr CSDL ti liu a phng tin.
Phm vi nghin cu:
- Tm hiu cng ngh web a phng tin
- Xy dng ng dng qun tr CSDL ti liu a phng tin cho website ca
trng
c, Tm tt c ng cc ni dung chnh v ng gp mi ca tc gi
2
Ni dung lun vn c trnh by lm 3 chng nh sau:
Chng 1 tm hiu v cng ngh web a phng tin, Tm hiu c cc cng ngh
pht trin web a phng tin nh l Tm hiu cng ngh PHP, cng ngh HTML5,
HTML5 l mt ngn ng c thit k thit lp ni dung web. N nhm lm cho vic
thit k v pht trin web d dng hn bng cch to mt giao din ngn ng nh du
chun ha v trc quan c bit, HTML5 c thm nhiu tnh nng c php mi. Chng
bao gm cc th mi nh <video>, <audio> v cc thnh phn <canvas>, cng nh s
tch hp ca ha ,
.
Chng 2, Kho st yu cu ca website trng HSPKT Hng yn.
Chng 3, xut xy dng gii php ng dng thc nghim qun tr CSDL ti liu
a phng tin cho website trng HSPKT Hng yn.
d, Phng php nghin cu
Tm hiu cc cng ngh web a phng tin nghin cu xy dng h qun tr
CSDL ti liu .
e, Kt lun
Lun vn t c nhng kt qu nht nh nh sau:
- Tm hiu c cng ngh web a phng tin
- Kho st v xy dng c h qun tr CSDL ti liu a phng tin cho website
ca trng HSPKT Hng yn
- Thc nghim ng dng h thng qun tr CSDL ti liu vo trong website ca
trng.
